&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Senior Analyst / Associate to sit at the intersection of finance, accounting, operations, and commercial strategy.&amp;nbsp; This cross-functional role sits on the Finance team and provides an entry point into any &amp;amp; all data that makes our business tick.&amp;nbsp; You’ll start with financial &amp;amp; operational data and expand into sales &amp;amp; marketing data.&amp;nbsp; Within a few months, we’ll want you to develop a full mental map of how the data flows across and between our systems, building expertise on which data is needed to answer which questions.&amp;nbsp; You’ll eventually provide input into how to improve our systems to improve data quality.&lt;/p&gt;
